  "time_ut": 1662093882,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Freeze assets of Sri Lankans associated with the LTTE",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "India's Enforcement Directorate on Thursday said it has frozen three immovable properties worth Rs 337 million belonging to Sri Lankan nationals linked to the LTTE in connection with a money laundering case.",
        "A bungalow in ECR and two agricultural lands belonging to Prema Kumar alias Gunasekaran in Tiruvannamalai district were also attached and his son Dileep alias Dileep was also attached, the official said.",
        "Gunasekaran was found to be involved in the 1999 assassination attempt of former Sri Lankan President Chandrika Bandaranaike Kumaratunga.",
        "This survival came to light when both of them illegally escaped from Sri Lanka and bought mansions and agricultural lands and settled there. Indian Q Division Police registered a case in this regard and investigated.",
        "It was also revealed that Gunasekaran had prepared fake identity cards, Aadhaar card, passport, driving license and PAN card with his son.",
        "It was revealed that Gunasekaran had links with international drug trafficking gangs and was arrested by the Tamil Nadu police for involvement in drug trafficking in 2011. After being imprisoned, Gunasekaran changed his identity and lived in hiding after his release.",
        "Subsequently, the Q Division Police recommended the Enforcement Department to take action against Gunasekaran under the Illegal Money Transfer Act. Based on that, the Central Enforcement Directorate registered a case against Gunasekaran.",
        "It is worth mentioning that currently Gunasekaran and his son Dilip are in Tiruchirappalli special camp. (R)"
      ],
